NAME

    Perl::PrereqScanner::Scanner::DistZilla::PluginBundle - scan for
    required plugins in Dist::Zilla plugin bundles

VERSION

    version 0.001

DESCRIPTION

    This scanner will look for the following indicators:

      * calls to the add_bundle method

      * calls to the add_plugins method

    Currently this only works for plugin bundles using the
    Dist::Zilla::Role::PluginBundle::Easy role.

BUGS

    Please report any bugs or feature requests on the bugtracker
    website
    https://rt.cpan.org/Public/Dist/Display.html?Name=Perl-PrereqScanner-Scanner-DistZilla-PluginBundle
    or by email to
    bug-Perl-PrereqScanner-Scanner-DistZilla-PluginBundle@rt.cpan.org
    <mailto:bug-Perl-PrereqScanner-Scanner-DistZilla-PluginBundle@rt.cpan.org>.

    When submitting a bug or request, please include a test-file or a
    patch to an existing test-file that illustrates the bug or
    desired feature.

